{
  "stem": "22869.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He lives here in town.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "He was an American citizen, and wasn't taken to Auschwitz until 1944.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he came in around-- I don't know, maybe in the midst of '44 to Auschwitz, to Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he found out I'm there, he sent a message for me, because he wanted to get some benefit of an old timer.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I met him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And one day, he notifies me that they're taking him away for a transport to a different camp.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Could I help him stay there?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He wants to be close to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I went to the supervisor there, and said, I was an old timer-- we usually had a little pull there.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I says, listen, maybe you can take this kid out, and substitute somebody else for him.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I know him from home, and so forth.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He says, I don't understand Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're talking so foolish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know none of us will come out alive here.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Maybe the place where he's going he has a chance in a million to stay alive.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why would you deny a person a chance like this?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it dawned on me, maybe the guy is right.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I went back to the fellow, and I told him, look, he promised me that he will take you out.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's all I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But he didn't-- of course, he didn't.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He left.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was liberated in January, a month later.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we met after the war, in Bratislava, and he hugged me on the street and kept on yelling, you saved my life by not having him taken out of there.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and I went through hell from now on.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "OK, let's get back to the subject matter.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have this meeting, and we decide, no, we're all going.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
